    <item>
      <title>Sending email from shell via mutt</title>
      <link>http://www.snowfrog.net/2012/10/09/sending-email-from-shell-via-mutt/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Oct 2012 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://www.snowfrog.net/2012/10/09/sending-email-from-shell-via-mutt/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;A quick example of sending email from the shell via mutt.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34; style=&#34;background: #202020&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;line-height: 125%&#34;&gt;% cat msg.txt 
pdf attached. Sonia.

&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;for &lt;/span&gt;i in *.pdf ; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;do              &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;mutt -s &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;pdf - $i&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; -a &lt;span style=&#34;color: #40ffff&#34;&gt;$i&lt;/span&gt; -- &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;foo@hotmail.com&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt; msg.txt
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;done&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;No rocket science, just saving me from RTFM&amp;rsquo;ing next time&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>reload mutt configuration</title>
      <link>http://www.snowfrog.net/2011/10/20/reload-mutt-configuration/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Oct 2011 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://www.snowfrog.net/2011/10/20/reload-mutt-configuration/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;To reload your &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.mutt.org/&#34;&gt;mutt&lt;/a&gt; configuration (for example after editing muttrc):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;:source /path/to/muttrc&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;:source /home/sonia/.muttrc&lt;/pre&gt;
</description>
